TITLE: General Configuration Example for Zed Assistant
DESCRIPTION: This comprehensive JSON configuration example demonstrates various settings for the Zed assistant, including enabled status, default model, feature-specific models, and panel settings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zed-industries/zed/blob/main/docs/src/assistant/configuration.md#2025-04-11_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "assistant": {
    "enabled": true,
    "default_model": {
      "provider": "zed.dev",
      "model": "claude-3-7-sonnet"
    },
    "editor_model": {
      "provider": "openai",
      "model": "gpt-4o"
    },
    "inline_assistant_model": {
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "model": "claude-3-5-sonnet"
    },
    "commit_message_model": {
      "provider": "openai",
      "model": "gpt-4o-mini"
    },
    "thread_summary_model": {
      "provider": "google",
      "model": "gemini-1.5-flash"
    },
    "version": "2",
    "button": true,
    "default_width": 480,
    "dock": "right"
  }
}
```

