TITLE: Configuring Custom clangd Binary Path in Zed
DESCRIPTION: This configuration specifies a custom path for the clangd binary and allows for additional command-line arguments. This is useful when you want to use a specific version of clangd not in the default system path.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zed-industries/zed/blob/main/docs/src/languages/cpp.md#2025-04-11_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "lsp": {
    "clangd": {
      "binary": {
        "path": "/path/to/clangd",
        "arguments": []
      }
    }
  }
}
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Configuring Ansible Language Server Settings in Zed
DESCRIPTION: JSON configuration for the Ansible language server in Zed settings. This should be added to the "lsp" section in ~/.zed/settings.json and includes settings for the ansible path, execution environment, Python interpreter path, and validation options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zed-industries/zed/blob/main/docs/src/languages/ansible.md#2025-04-11_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
"lsp": {
  // Note, the Zed Ansible extension prefixes all settings with `ansible`
  // so instead of using `ansible.ansible.path` use `ansible.path`.
  "ansible-language-server": {
    "settings": {
      "ansible": {
        "path": "ansible"
      },
      "executionEnvironment": {
        "enabled": false
      },
      "python": {
        "interpreterPath": "python3"
      },
      "validation": {
        "enabled": true,
        // To enable linting, manually install ansible-lint and make sure it is your PATH
        "lint": {
          "enabled": true,
          "path": "ansible-lint"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Configuring elm-language-server in Zed Settings
DESCRIPTION: Example JSON configuration for elm-language-server in Zed's settings.json. Shows how to customize initialization options like disabling ELS diagnostics, updating diagnostics behavior, and setting elm-review diagnostic level.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zed-industries/zed/blob/main/docs/src/languages/elm.md#2025-04-11_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "lsp": {
    "elm-language-server": {
      "initialization_options": {
        "disableElmLSDiagnostics": true,
        "onlyUpdateDiagnosticsOnSave": false,
        "elmReviewDiagnostics": "warning"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

