TITLE: Registering Tree-sitter Grammars in TOML
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to register Tree-sitter grammars in the extension.toml file. This includes specifying the repository URL and the Git revision to use for the grammar.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zed-industries/zed/blob/main/docs/src/extensions/languages.md#2025-04-11_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: toml
CODE:
```
[grammars.gleam]
repository = "https://github.com/gleam-lang/tree-sitter-gleam"
rev = "58b7cac8fc14c92b0677c542610d8738c373fa81"
```

