TITLE: Detecting Runnable Scripts in JSON Files (Scheme)
DESCRIPTION: This scheme snippet from the runnables.scm file for JSON defines rules for detecting runnable scripts in package.json and composer.json files. It captures script names and sets tags for package and composer scripts.
