TITLE: JSON Schema LSP Settings Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for JSON Language Server settings to associate schemas with specific file patterns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zed-industries/zed/blob/main/docs/src/languages/json.md#2025-04-11_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
"lsp": {
  "json-language-server": {
    "settings": {
      "json": {
        "schemas": [
          {
            "fileMatch": ["*/*.luarc.json"],
            "url": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sumneko/vscode-lua/master/setting/schema.json"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
```

