TITLE: Python Function Example in Markdown
DESCRIPTION: Example showing syntax highlighted Python code block in Markdown with a fibonacci function using function decorator.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zed-industries/zed/blob/main/docs/src/languages/markdown.md#2025-04-11_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
import functools as ft

@ft.lru_cache(maxsize=500)
def fib(n):
    return n if n < 2 else fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)
```

